Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.78,0:00:03.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k178}命运也是推理的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k162}神秘的事件也能看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.06,0:00:07.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}失踪了的名犬 道尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.50,0:00:09.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k144}养狗爱好者们意外的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.94,0:00:11.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k243}唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.48,0:00:13.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.39,0:00:15.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}Something's just not right
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.41,0:00:21.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在找寻着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.46,0:00:26.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已经习惯了谎言 现在也是一样 fake your eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.45,0:00:32.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}The start of century
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没有能够确定的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.22,0:00:41.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使一个人也不能哭泣 软弱 hate myself
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.55,0:00:51.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}与真实的痛苦相反的是 埋藏在心中的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.53,0:00:59.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在 映射出来 朝着两个人所决定的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.12,0:01:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I think it's only my destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}朝着没有尽头的黑暗前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.22,0:01:13.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那里有未知的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.51,0:01:18.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Oh yeah. You're going nowhere. It's only destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}切实地前行着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.77,0:01:28.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}感受现在 you're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.72,0:01:46.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为要搬家 想把一些没用的东西送给熟人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.48,0:01:50.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们来到了阿笠博士的友人加纳照也家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.31,0:01:54.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}加纳的友人 纲岛吉雄先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.95,0:01:57.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}土佐林亚纪小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.23,0:01:59.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}和莲树志乃小姐也在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.94,0:02:04.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k272}在讨论从屋子里拿什么东西回去的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.12,0:02:09.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}屋子里的一只名叫道尔的蝴蝶犬失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.34,0:02:17.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}后来在焚烧炉中发现了道尔的项圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被小刀切断 并且烧焦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.65,0:02:22.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不…不会吧…那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}道尔的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.16,0:02:27.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}不会的…不可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.08,0:02:34.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦 奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k214}刚才看的时候蓝色的坐垫有两张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}加上亚瑟叼来那张的话是三张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}多了一张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.52,0:02:57.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}无法消灭的证据（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}道尔在听到中午12点的钟声敲响之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就立刻跑到和室吃点心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.73,0:03:09.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k221}从此消失了踪影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k255}之后我们所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.63,0:03:16.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}就跟着加纳先生到厨房去拿了奶酪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.78,0:03:20.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接着到了和室 才发现道尔失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.59,0:03:23.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}之后大家就在屋子里面分头找了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.05,0:03:25.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}按照屋子的平面图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k232}虽然不清楚谁找过什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.76,0:03:33.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过犯人会将道尔藏在什么地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.02,0:03:38.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还有 他又打算怎样将它带离这个地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.32,0:03:42.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你们搬家的事情可能得延后了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.27,0:03:43.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.24,0:03:45.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k197}搬家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.94,0:03:51.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}你说因为要搬家 所以才要把这些东西送给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那我们今天可以带回去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k283}当然可以了 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k207}那其他人也是今天要拿回去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.11,0:03:59.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k235}不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.06,0:04:01.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k95}纲岛先生要的挂钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}我明天会亲自送到他家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k269}至于莲木小姐的音响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.56,0:04:07.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k125}只要在我十天后 搬家的前一天送去就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过我平常也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k142}应该可以立刻就帮她送过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}他们今天之所以会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k149}是因为我说柜子里面也许还会再找出古董
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k241}他们才会来看看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k218}没想到土佐林小姐会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.78,0:04:24.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k189}还急得今天就想要把那个花瓶给带回去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个花瓶 好像就是放在客厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.82,0:04:28.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}难道说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.34,0:04:32.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}道尔会在那里面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}想想也不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}至于十天之后才要送去的那套音响里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.24,0:04:45.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}也不可能放任何的动物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.11,0:04:48.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}更别说和室的挂钟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k286}要把狗藏在里面根本是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}奇怪 那个挂钟慢了整整五分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.33,0:05:00.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.75,0:05:02.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k141}它才修过 应该不会慢才对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.97,0:05:04.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k125}我刚才看的时候明明是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.07,0:05:11.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个像棉花的是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.73,0:05:13.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k166}好像是某种化学纤维
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个让我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.19,0:05:18.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k223}这种会闪闪发亮的棉花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.53,0:05:25.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k211}在刚才亚瑟叼来的那个蓝色坐垫里面也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.56,0:05:27.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k131}我好像在哪里也看过这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.86,0:05:32.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是焚化炉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你要干嘛 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.48,0:05:42.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}道尔不会真的被丢到里面烧死了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}刚才看到的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}还以为这只是燃烧之后剩下的垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.52,0:05:49.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k242}现在我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k118}其实这是玻璃棉 是一种吸音材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}原来犯人是用了那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.73,0:05:59.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}我已经知道道尔在哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.45,0:06:05.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}也知道了犯人把它藏起来的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.35,0:06:06.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}甚至他的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}还有他的身份都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}都已经这么晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}我也该告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.01,0:06:20.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那我也要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}我还得回去准备晚饭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}你们再等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.51,0:06:29.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k202}你就当流年不利吧 别再想那只狗就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.18,0:06:35.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个声音是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}这是和室里的钟声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}那个挂钟只有在中午12点才会敲响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.56,0:06:43.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k278}到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.31,0:06:49.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.52,0:06:52.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}还蛮顺利的哦 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.57,0:06:56.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k206}那我们现在就去客厅做准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.15,0:06:58.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}准备什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}我们现在要来做个实验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}看看犯人能不能在不知不觉的情况下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.09,0:07:08.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k273}把道尔藏在一个大家都找不到的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.94,0:07:09.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.02,0:07:12.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k108}道尔到现在都还没有找到 实验什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.22,0:07:13.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k87}这个实验的主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.17,0:07:18.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}自然非道尔不可了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.76,0:07:20.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}道尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.93,0:07:23.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}终于找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.29,0:07:34.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那我们现在就快来实验吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个实验就从道尔在我们面前消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}玄关前的走廊开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.01,0:07:46.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的 既然狗都已经找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k298}还这么麻烦干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.31,0:07:52.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k133}我也没有时间陪这些小鬼头玩侦探游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}别这样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.22,0:07:57.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}好了 光彦 现在可以开始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.39,0:07:59.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.26,0:08:04.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}又响了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.01,0:08:11.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 刚才道尔就是听到钟声之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}像平常一样 跑向了能吃到奶酪的和室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而我们则是先绕到了厨房才走到和室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.86,0:08:19.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没有错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.96,0:08:24.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这么一来 你想道尔现在会在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么白痴问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}道尔既然每次都在和室里吃点心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}现在自然会在和室里啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}奇怪 怎么不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.12,0:08:40.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且 刚才的钟声也不是从这里发出来的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.72,0:08:41.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}奇怪了 怎么会这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.45,0:08:46.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}加纳先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.78,0:08:49.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}钟声是从客厅传出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.62,0:08:51.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}客厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}难道说…钟声是从音响的扩音器里传出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.82,0:08:58.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.90,0:09:02.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k108}是我们刚才把在和室敲响的钟声录下来之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}又用这套音响把它放出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.38,0:09:08.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k282}先拿了哥哥房里的录音机来用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.35,0:09:13.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那道尔听到钟声以后就跑到客厅来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.54,0:09:16.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只有钟声的话还不够 还得有坐垫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.75,0:09:17.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}坐垫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k135}对啊 你不是说道尔吃点心的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.46,0:09:23.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k237}每次都会自己叼出一个坐垫给自己坐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.54,0:09:27.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是道尔最喜欢的蓝色坐垫刚才在和室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.39,0:09:31.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其实道尔并不是喜欢蓝色的坐垫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}狗的听力是人类的四倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}鼻子的嗅觉也的确要比人类灵敏很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是它们的眼睛几乎没有办法辨识颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以道尔每次吃点心的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}抽的只是沾有自己味道的坐垫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只是那个坐垫碰巧是蓝色的罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.41,0:09:54.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是说 道尔并不是在12点的时候才到和室里去等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.66,0:09:59.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而是以为只要在钟声的旁边 放上它惯用的坐垫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要不了多久它就有点心可以吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以犯人就巧妙地利用了这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}把道尔给引到客厅来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}至于道尔每次惯用的坐垫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k232}上面会有咬过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}犯人很轻易地就能辨识出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}这也不对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}刚才我跟纲岛显示就先到客厅来找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是什么也没看到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}也没有什么坐垫跟狗 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么会有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.58,0:10:28.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k107}有个地方很好藏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你看 在这音响的后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k276}还有这么个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是在扩音器的后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.93,0:10:50.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人其实早就将扩音器内侧的吸音材料事先拨开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.76,0:10:54.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接着再把垫子放到多出来的空间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}再把奶酪放到上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.46,0:11:00.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k262}当然 右边的扩音器做了这种装置之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k273}自然不能让它发出声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.83,0:11:05.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}接着 他只要将他事先录下来的钟声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.99,0:11:07.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}从左边的扩音器放出来的话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.22,0:11:11.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}道尔自然会受到坐垫和奶酪的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还有钟声这三个因素吸引
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}靠着嗅觉跑到板子被敲开的扩音器那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}吃它每天都会吃到的奶酪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.20,0:11:21.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}但是 它要是把奶酪吃完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}不就该出来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k158}吃完以后它就睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k249}因为犯人事先将安眠药塞进了奶酪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.11,0:11:30.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}不过事情真的会这么顺利吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.04,0:11:34.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}你别忘了 那个时候和室那边的钟声啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一到12点的时候也会敲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.90,0:11:39.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其实钟声根本就没有响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.55,0:11:43.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}因为那个钟走的根本是半夜的12点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为和室的挂钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.71,0:11:49.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k142}已经被调整到只会在中午12点的时候才会响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.18,0:11:52.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只要事先将里面的时针转过12个小时的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.66,0:11:53.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}钟声自然就不会响了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}可是到底是谁会这样做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这还用问吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.44,0:12:02.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}除了要将这套音响拿走的莲木小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.56,0:12:04.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看也想不出第二个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.04,0:12:06.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k121}你是想让那只狗跑进扩音器里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.63,0:12:11.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k239}就可以将它偷出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.49,0:12:14.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k285}可是 我没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.46,0:12:16.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k297}你不要这么快下定论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.24,0:12:19.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k178}莲木小姐绝对不可能做这种事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.17,0:12:23.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}可是 刚才她的鞋子明明就掉在焚化炉的旁边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k84}你错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}犯人并不是莲木小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.89,0:12:37.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人并不是莲木小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.51,0:12:40.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k262}你在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.32,0:12:45.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k281}但是 那套音响要十天以后才会送去给莲木小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.53,0:12:49.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她怎么可能会笨到把一个动物藏在里面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 如果不是莲木小姐的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}犯人干嘛要把狗藏在扩音器里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.51,0:12:57.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k237}其实这个犯人并不是想把道尔偷出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.07,0:13:01.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他只不过是想暂时把道尔藏起来罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.65,0:13:02.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}暂时把它藏起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}可是就算这是个死角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.60,0:13:09.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k148}我们还是会很快发现扩音器的板子被拆掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.51,0:13:12.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到时候就会立刻检查音响里面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.58,0:13:17.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以这个犯人才会立刻走到客厅来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.80,0:13:20.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}先把板子重新放回去 再将道尔藏起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.81,0:13:22.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我说的没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k145}纲岛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果第一个到这里来找的就是你的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.02,0:13:31.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在这里做做样子将板子放回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k203}对你来说根本不难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.57,0:13:35.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.32,0:13:37.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k75}你的确是先到音响的后面看过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k245}还说道尔不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想叔叔你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}也许是从加纳先生的父母亲那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.23,0:13:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k198}知道道尔吃点心时候的习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.71,0:13:51.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}又知道他们平时根本没怎么用这套音响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以呢 他就利用之前来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.32,0:13:58.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}先把扩音器的吸音材料剥掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.79,0:14:00.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k247}再将板子拆开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k206}为今天要将道尔藏起来的计划做准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样以后在音响里动手脚的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.94,0:14:09.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}扩音器就不会发出奇怪的声音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你只要在道尔吃点心的时候来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.41,0:14:14.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}也就能够事先录下钟声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}至于你是什么时候将胶带跟坐垫放到扩音器里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.15,0:14:21.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}应该是12点之前莲木小姐来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k294}我们全都跑到玄关去迎接她的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.94,0:14:29.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后你假意装作找寻失踪的道尔的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.51,0:14:30.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}绕到了扩音器的后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.04,0:14:34.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}将项圈从睡着的道尔身上拆下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}将坐垫拿出来之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k169}就将板子重新盖上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k235}之后只要将坐垫放回和室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k271}把挂钟拨快的时针拨回原来的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}再将项圈丢进焚化炉烧掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k219}把后门打开之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.94,0:14:52.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k242}在不知情的人眼中看来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.77,0:14:56.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}自然就会以为是有人抱了道尔从后门跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}纲岛先生也企图将剥下来的吸音材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k268}丢进焚化炉里企图灭迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是玻璃棉本来就具有隔热的功效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.64,0:15:10.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以才会没被烧掉 全留在焚化炉里面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.61,0:15:11.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k297}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.86,0:15:14.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k125}难怪我们让亚瑟去找道尔的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}它会从和室里把坐垫叼出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来是犯人早就将坐垫放回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.06,0:15:24.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是亚瑟怎么会闻不出道尔在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.71,0:15:27.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}道尔明明就在扩音器里面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它知道它在那里 只是它进不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.33,0:15:33.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k251}因为它以前曾在这个房间里被主人骂得很凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.69,0:15:39.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过小弟弟 我把道尔藏在扩音器里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.53,0:15:41.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对我根本就没有好处嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.90,0:15:44.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k237}叔叔 我想你真正想要的并不是道尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k277}而是道尔项圈上镶的…这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是这个宝石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.36,0:15:53.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是加纳先生的爷爷从法国买回来的宝石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k271}而且还价值不菲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你从哪找到的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}就在和室的挂钟的钟摆上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.32,0:16:06.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个挂钟在12点的时候时间还很正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是到了三点却慢了三分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.74,0:16:09.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}五点时就慢了五分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}每隔一个小时它就会往后延迟一分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以我才想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}那个钟摆的后面一定是贴上了什么别的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}会将它贴在钟摆上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.16,0:16:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k221}自然只有计划将挂钟拿走的纲岛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.59,0:16:26.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是你没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.14,0:16:28.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k255}可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.16,0:16:29.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k102}纲岛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.98,0:16:53.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.81,0:17:04.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}亚瑟 快放开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你没有办法挥拳打狗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}叔叔 因为你是那么喜欢狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.35,0:17:14.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k247}所以你才会没有把道尔给杀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.91,0:17:17.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k256}你之所以没有把扩音器的板子用螺丝锁死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k285}就是为了让道尔在醒来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k171}能够轻易地走出扩音器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.66,0:17:23.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k218}对不对 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过 纲岛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.77,0:17:28.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}你为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.91,0:17:31.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}全是为了钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.49,0:17:35.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k158}为了养得起我家越来越多的狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}自然需要一大笔钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.62,0:17:40.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}既然这样 你卖掉几条狗负担不就少了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.77,0:17:44.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是我家养的那些狗几乎都是人家丢掉的杂种狗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.33,0:17:48.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不要说是卖了 想送都送不出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.89,0:17:52.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}再这样下去它们将来就只有饿死在路边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要不然就是被毒死…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.72,0:17:57.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k181}除此之外根本没有别的出路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}纲岛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.57,0:18:02.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k289}纲岛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.11,0:18:04.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k254}拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k241}这个你尽管拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.15,0:18:10.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}我并不是要把这颗宝石给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.55,0:18:17.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k275}而是要送给你们家的那些可爱的狗狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.09,0:18:21.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}加纳老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.11,0:18:26.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你也不用这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k289}我这么做 我想我爷爷一定也会很高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.26,0:19:05.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}会失去什么 即使现在开始 无所谓吧 能做得到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.39,0:19:15.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}尝试自己想做的事吧 直到与你相遇为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.48,0:19:22.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}虽然什么都没有 闭上眼睛却能看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.78,0:19:27.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有个与你一起生活的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.58,0:19:33.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}always 将爱藏于胸口鼓起勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.08,0:19:38.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使失败也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.59,0:19:43.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}No 那并非所有的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.05,0:19:49.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Yes 趁风向转变的现在向前飞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他的脸皮也真够厚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.58,0:20:15.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}让一个缺乏管理能力的人养狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.74,0:20:17.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}那些狗太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.76,0:20:18.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k203}好了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k93}他都已经答应不会再让狗增加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.96,0:20:24.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过亚瑟跟克丽丝真的好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k278}它们还会在犯人要逃走的时候夹击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.85,0:20:28.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}跟警犬一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.52,0:20:29.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k167}这是本能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.60,0:20:34.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}亚瑟只是想要制服将它主人推开的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.34,0:20:36.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}至于克丽丝 原本就是一只牧羊犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.74,0:20:39.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这种古英国牧羊犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.51,0:20:40.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k177}向来就被训练成能将走散的绵羊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.33,0:20:43.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k181}再度赶回羊群里面的本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它在看到有人先冲出去的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.03,0:20:50.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k198}就会下意识的先到前面挡着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.13,0:20:52.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你也太不浪漫了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过我还是搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.69,0:20:58.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}莲木小姐的那双鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.23,0:21:01.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}又怎么会被放在焚化炉的前面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.14,0:21:05.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想啊 这一定是它搞的鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.88,0:21:08.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你们先躲在这里一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.73,0:21:09.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}干嘛啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.08,0:21:15.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.44,0:21:18.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}亚瑟 不要乱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.08,0:21:22.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}你什么时候学会这种恶作剧的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.58,0:21:25.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}亚瑟 你有没有在听啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.23,0:21:27.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}亚瑟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.40,0:21:31.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k218}它是不是讨厌我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.23,0:21:34.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k283}不 它是希望你能够一直留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.60,0:21:36.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对不对 亚瑟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}刚才你跟我们说 以前要出去散步的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.76,0:21:44.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}亚瑟都会先把你的鞋子叼出来等你对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.16,0:21:46.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那是因为亚瑟知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.39,0:21:50.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k123}人类一定要先穿上了鞋子才能够出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.57,0:21:53.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以说 为了不让莲木小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.18,0:21:56.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}把它最喜欢的克丽丝带回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.58,0:21:59.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它才会把你的鞋子藏到别的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.84,0:22:01.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.32,0:22:06.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过你不用担心了 亚瑟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.68,0:22:08.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为我跟克丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.23,0:22:11.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}以后也要跟你的主人一起到伦敦去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.20,0:22:12.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}我们可以一直在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.94,0:22:16.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这么说 你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.91,0:22:18.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k297}对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.34,0:22:21.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k143}其实我今天就是来回复这件事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.87,0:22:26.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这么说 你们两个真的打算要结婚了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.58,0:22:28.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这真是喜事一桩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.72,0:22:30.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k214}恭喜你们这对新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.56,0:22:33.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k285}恭喜你们两个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.62,0:22:36.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k206}在你们搬家之前还得好好庆祝一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.25,0:22:39.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你真傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.66,0:22:44.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k241}没有人生你的气 你尽管放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.03,0:22:49.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.88,0:22:53.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们一直好担心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.69,0:22:55.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k181}因为你一直都无精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.41,0:22:58.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k272}所以我们最近一直在讨论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.72,0:23:00.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k231}要怎么样才能让你恢复精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.72,0:23:02.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我怎么都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.98,0:23:06.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}因为谁叫你每次都要跟灰原同学斗嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.80,0:23:07.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没错没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.16,0:23:08.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k137}是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.27,0:23:11.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k211}太好了 亚瑟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.14,0:23:14.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}这可是大功一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.12,0:23:24.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对对 永远保持这个表情就对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.28,0:23:27.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看到你摆出这样的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.99,0:23:29.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}别人才会以为你是个孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.94,0:23:35.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不然怎么看都像是个七老八十的老太婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.25,0:23:38.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.70,0:23:39.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k144}很无礼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.05,0:23:41.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}是八十四岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.98,0:23:46.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}兰 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.99,0:23:49.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}兰 给我们拍张照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.54,0:23:52.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}拍了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.38,0:24:02.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.52,0:24:04.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k114}给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.20,0:24:06.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}元 我是毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.97,0:24:09.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k177}出了什么事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.23,0:24:11.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.81,0:24:14.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k159}南纪白滨神秘之旅（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.45,0:24:17.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.63,0:24:20.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k218}车钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.09,0:24:21.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k246}下回是旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.97,0:24:24.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k88}旅行 旅行 旅行 旅行…
